description: Welcome to the East Side of South Boston! This sunny and spacious 2 bed 1 bath home is in an amazing location w/ plenty of amenities. The seamless flow of the open-concept kitchen and living room is perfect for entertaining. Another focal point of the home is the private rear deck and an extra flex/office space located right off of the kitchen. Both bedrooms are appointed with custom closets while gleaming hardwood floors span throughout the home. Additional features include central air, in-unit washer/dryer, pet friendly building, low condo fees, and private storage. Enjoy living in this incredibly walkable location just steps away from Medal of Honor Park, M St Beach and the numerous shops and restaurants throughout Southie. Don't miss out on this home! Open House this weekend Sunday Noon-1:30pm
